        explain: "The identifier resolved to a definition that is not declared `pub`, and the call site lives in a different module file. Stage1 punch list Gap 2 — once the parser splices imported items into the world module, the type checker enforces file-private visibility for non-pub items: a private helper in file_a.hexa is invisible to file_b.hexa even when file_b imports file_a. Fix: add `pub` to the definition, or move the caller into the defining module.",
