        explain: "Two different files declare `pub` items with the same name. Pub items live in the global namespace once the world module is assembled (Stage1 punch list Gap 2 — multi-file pivot), so two pub `greet`s collide just like two definitions in the same file would. Fix: rename one of the definitions, or remove `pub` from the helper that should remain file-private.",
        fix_it_kind: FixItKind::Replace
